The FAQ section must contain 6 questions with 40-60 word answers each. Questions and sources:

1. "How much does a 4 bedroom apartment cost in Orlando?" — Source: PAA. Answer must cite $2,200-$3,800 range with product type note.
2. "Are there cheap 4 bedroom apartments in Orlando?" — Source: PAA. Answer must cite the Kissimmee corridor and West Orlando (MetroWest, Apopka) as the most affordable submarkets, note that $2,200-$2,400/month is achievable for townhome product in these areas.
